1
00:00:11,000 --> 00:00:13,080
You once asked me

2
00:00:13,080 --> 00:00:16,520
if I could paint "A Thousand Li of Rivers and Mountains" with you.

3
00:00:16,520 --> 00:00:18,280
That day,

4
00:00:18,280 --> 00:00:21,200
my dreams gained color.

5
00:00:21,200 --> 00:00:24,160
I was just a lowly painter at the Hanlin Art Academy,

6
00:00:24,160 --> 00:00:27,560
while you were the Emperor, looked up to by the world.

7
00:00:27,560 --> 00:00:29,240
You are my master,

8
00:00:29,240 --> 00:00:31,200
my Brother Ji,

9
00:00:31,200 --> 00:00:33,760
and my only confidant.

10
00:00:33,760 --> 00:00:37,360
Now that the thousand li of rivers and mountains are on paper,

11
00:00:37,360 --> 00:00:40,480
for this final stroke,

12
00:00:40,480 --> 00:00:41,440
I want to use

13
00:00:43,480 --> 00:00:46,480
your blood to paint it.

14
00:00:52,560 --> 00:00:55,560
This painting of "Auspicious Cranes" by Your Majesty

15
00:00:55,560 --> 00:00:57,560
is indeed a sign of good fortune.

16
00:00:58,480 --> 00:01:01,280
But what is fake is fake after all.

17
00:01:01,840 --> 00:01:03,200
In my humble opinion,

18
00:01:03,440 --> 00:01:06,960
the vast territory of our Great Song is maintained by governance,

19
00:01:06,960 --> 00:01:08,560
not by painting.

20
00:01:10,560 --> 00:01:11,560
Well said.

21
00:01:13,360 --> 00:01:15,490
A thousand li of rivers and mountains.

22
00:01:16,800 --> 00:01:18,800
Only the heavens are above,

23
00:01:19,880 --> 00:01:21,680
no mountains are equal to it.

24
00:01:22,920 --> 00:01:27,480
This monthly exam at the Hanlin Art Academy takes landscape as its theme.

25
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:30,600
It is truly wonderful.

26
00:01:33,560 --> 00:01:35,620
If the Art Academy is not a fairyland,

27
00:01:36,120 --> 00:01:38,720
why would young birds leap onto the high beams?

28
00:01:40,560 --> 00:01:41,600
One day,

29
00:01:42,200 --> 00:01:43,720
I will be like this bird,

30
00:01:44,479 --> 00:01:46,140
and fly over these high walls.

31
00:01:47,759 --> 00:01:49,280
The Hanlin Painting Academy

32
00:01:49,280 --> 00:01:52,610
is the dream destination for all painters in the Great Song.

33
00:01:52,960 --> 00:01:55,759
The painters here are all exceptionally skilled.

34
00:01:56,039 --> 00:01:58,240
Some paint while dancing.

35
00:01:59,039 --> 00:02:00,920
Some paint with both hands.

36
00:02:03,480 --> 00:02:05,840
Some paint by divination.

37
00:02:06,640 --> 00:02:09,440
Some paint blindfolded.

38
00:02:10,240 --> 00:02:12,570
It is currently time for the monthly exam.

39
00:02:12,960 --> 00:02:13,760
In a few days,

40
00:02:14,440 --> 00:02:16,500
the triennial grand exam will begin.

41
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:19,640
If I can take first place in this exam,

42
00:02:20,320 --> 00:02:22,000
I'll receive personal instruction from the Emperor.

43
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:23,640
We have to submit our paintings tomorrow.

44
00:02:23,640 --> 00:02:25,440
How can you be sleeping here?

45
00:02:26,800 --> 00:02:27,800
No rush.

46
00:02:28,720 --> 00:02:30,320
Let me sleep for a bit.

47
00:02:31,640 --> 00:02:32,840
After I wake up,

48
00:02:34,040 --> 00:02:37,360
I'll simply paint the scenery from my dream.

49
00:02:39,120 --> 00:02:42,320
I will definitely get into the Hanlin Painting Academy.

50
00:02:50,120 --> 00:02:52,040
It's you again, you bastard.

51
00:02:52,960 --> 00:02:54,720
Look closely, everyone.

52
00:02:54,760 --> 00:02:56,960
His name is Ximeng.

53
00:02:57,320 --> 00:02:59,040
He has no parents.

54
00:02:59,720 --> 00:03:02,320
He grew up in the Ciyou Bureau.

55
00:03:02,720 --> 00:03:05,440
Somehow, he caught Prime Minister Cai's eye.

56
00:03:05,920 --> 00:03:09,960
He really is an ant in the mud trying to climb high.

57
00:03:12,560 --> 00:03:15,160
I don't recall such a person in our Art Academy.

58
00:03:15,520 --> 00:03:17,560
Where did Prime Minister Cai recommend him to?

59
00:03:17,560 --> 00:03:19,400
The Imperial Archives.

60
00:03:19,680 --> 00:03:22,680
What's he doing at the Archives?

61
00:03:24,320 --> 00:03:27,480
Emptying chamber pots for the old clerks.

62
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:32,610
He's not content with just emptying pots.

63
00:03:33,079 --> 00:03:36,480
He often sneaks into our Hanlin Art Academy to steal painting techniques.

64
00:03:36,480 --> 00:03:38,010
Playing with these stones.

65
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:40,200
A bastard is a bastard.

66
00:03:40,480 --> 00:03:41,680
No one raised you right.

67
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:42,480
Stop.

68
00:03:46,960 --> 00:03:48,960
Sharp needles hidden deep in grass,

69
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:52,200
now rising above the weeds.

70
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:54,040
You've gone too far.

71
00:04:03,240 --> 00:04:04,240
Are you okay?

72
00:04:12,320 --> 00:04:13,360
I heard

73
00:04:14,480 --> 00:04:17,880
the annual painter exam follows the monthly test.

74
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:20,850
You sneak in to learn every day.

75
00:04:22,720 --> 00:04:24,050
Do you want to take part?

76
00:04:31,840 --> 00:04:32,640
Alright then.

77
00:04:33,440 --> 00:04:35,680
Since it's such a fine day today,

78
00:04:37,159 --> 00:04:40,090
why don't I hold an apprenticeship ceremony for you?

79
00:04:40,640 --> 00:04:42,040
Let them take a good look.

80
00:05:03,720 --> 00:05:05,520
If this rope is pulled to the end,

81
00:05:05,640 --> 00:05:07,440
your hands will be ruined.

82
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:09,840
Oh dear, without hands,

83
00:05:09,960 --> 00:05:12,320
how will you paint in the future?

84
00:05:21,920 --> 00:05:24,640
So this is what despair looks like.

85
00:05:27,400 --> 00:05:28,680
Beg me.

86
00:05:28,840 --> 00:05:30,680
It's not too late.

87
00:05:32,040 --> 00:05:33,840
Quickly, beg our Young Master.

88
00:05:34,320 --> 00:05:35,320
Beg him!

89
00:05:35,720 --> 00:05:36,960
Beg me.

90
00:05:38,280 --> 00:05:39,520
Beg our Young Master.

91
00:05:43,720 --> 00:05:45,800
Beg me.

92
00:05:56,880 --> 00:05:58,280
Hanlin Painting Academy

93
00:05:58,480 --> 00:06:00,320
is not a place for an ant like you.

94
00:06:00,880 --> 00:06:02,720
I have no intention of fighting for a position.

95
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:03,880
I just want to paint,

96
00:06:04,080 --> 00:06:06,040
to preserve the beauty of the world on paper.

97
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:08,840
What does the world's beauty have to do with ants?

98
00:06:09,200 --> 00:06:11,920
Ants should stick to moving dirt and sand.

99
00:06:12,520 --> 00:06:13,640
When someone tosses you a scrap,

100
00:06:13,640 --> 00:06:15,000
scramble to eat it.

101
00:06:15,280 --> 00:06:18,480
The birds are free to view the vast mountains and rivers.

102
00:06:19,080 --> 00:06:21,010
Since birds survey the landscape,

103
00:06:21,200 --> 00:06:23,400
why focus on a few mere ants?

104
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:27,080
What a sharp-tongued ant.

105
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:30,770
Then let me make this clear.

106
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:33,480
If you try to enter the Painting Academy again,

107
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:36,920
it won't be your brush I break next time.

108
00:06:38,400 --> 00:06:40,520
It's been ten years.

109
00:06:40,520 --> 00:06:42,120
This grudge,

110
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:44,480
I must avenge it.

111
00:06:44,480 --> 00:06:46,960
As long as I can enter the Hanlin Painting Academy,

112
00:06:46,960 --> 00:06:48,800
become the Chief Painter,

113
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:50,680
and see the Emperor,

114
00:06:50,680 --> 00:06:52,720
everything will end.

115
00:06:53,680 --> 00:06:54,480
Your Majesty,

116
00:06:55,040 --> 00:06:57,800
you only care about the Painting Academy all day.

117
00:06:58,080 --> 00:06:59,740
You keep a group of noble sons,

118
00:06:59,920 --> 00:07:02,600
not letting them take the exams or advise you.

119
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:04,600
Instead, you indulge in painting and calligraphy,

120
00:07:04,600 --> 00:07:08,000
or wear strange costumes in the other courtyard

121
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:09,480
to play games.

122
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:14,800
Is this how a diligent ruler should behave, Your Majesty?

123
00:07:15,520 --> 00:07:16,800
Your Majesty.

124
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:26,120
Are you saying that just because I painted a few pictures,

125
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:29,080
I have neglected state affairs?

126
00:07:29,080 --> 00:07:31,610
Is my reign inferior to the previous dynasty?

127
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:39,400
Do you know why I established the Hanlin Painting Academy?

128
00:07:40,760 --> 00:07:42,280
I

129
00:07:42,280 --> 00:07:46,440
only want to paint this hard-won vast landscape.

130
00:07:49,159 --> 00:07:49,960
But none of you

131
00:07:53,159 --> 00:07:55,220
understand my painstaking efforts.

132
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:36,640
Who came up with such an idea?

133
00:08:36,640 --> 00:08:39,200
Using the light reflected by this bronze mirror

134
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:42,919
to paint the fleeting mountains.
